      "writtenOn": "2020-06-17T01:16:48Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This only works if |root| is in the DOM. If it\u0027s not attached,\nthis will fail. Perhaps we should rewrite all of these to not\ndepend on querySelectorAll?",
      "revId": "99136755943a4480ddb10b51c7d319d9423042e0",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
