      "writtenOn": "2020-06-25T03:35:07Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Awesome investigation! It is indeed inconvenient not to have something that returns all the child elements including root. If we add a util function, it might be a bit inefficient because we essentially need to copy all the elements in NodeList\u003cElement\u003e out to another list.",
      "parentUuid": "a248d66e_54703847",
      "revId": "99136755943a4480ddb10b51c7d319d9423042e0",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
